text: KUDL may refer to: * KWOD, a radio station (1660 AM) licensed to Kansas City, Kansas, United States, known as KUDL from 2011 to 2014 * KMBZ-FM, a radio station (98.1 FM) licensed to Kansas City, Kansas, United States, known as KUDL-FM and KUDL from 1969 to 2011 * KCNW, a radio station (1380 AM) licensed to Fairway, Kansas, United States, known as KUDL from 1953 to 1975
title: KUDL (disambiguation)
